name: Steamed spare ribs in black bean sauce
ingredients:
- Spare ribs: 660g
- Garlic: 2 cloves
- Sugar: 1.5 teaspoons
- Black bean sauce: 1.5 teaspoons
- Cornflour: 2 teaspoons
- Salt: 0.5 teaspoons
- Soya sauce: 1 teaspoon
- Sesame oil: A drizzle
steps:
- Cut spare ribs into 1 inch chunks and mix all ingredients well. Add splash of water. Marinade overnight
- Steam for 45 minutes at 80%. Check. May need another 10 minutes.
- To reheat steam for 15 minutes
